          <span>How do credit cards work?</span>
          <h3>Credit cards allow you to make purchases online, in stores, and pay bills with ease and convenience.</h3>
          <p>When you use a credit card, the bank pays the merchant on your behalf. You then repay the bank either in full or over time, with possible interest charges.</p>

          <ul class="payment-box-list">
            <li><i class="flaticon-check"></i> Use it anywhere that accepts credit cards, online or offline.</li>
            <li><i class="flaticon-check"></i> Make payments instantly or carry a balance with interest.</li>
            <li><i class="flaticon-check"></i> Benefit from purchase protections and fraud monitoring.</li>
            <li><i class="flaticon-check"></i> Access rewards, cashback, and other perks based on your usage.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="payment-box-image">
          <img src="/assets/img/payment-box.png" alt="image">
        </div>
